snippet: The Senate’s final week in session this year promises to be memorable for something less inspired than its accomplishments: the vast amount of time it spends doing nothing in particular.
abstract: Senate prepares to wrap up a sluggish 2013, year memorable not for body's legislation but for its inaction.
lead_paragraph: The Senate’s final week in session this year promises to be memorable for something less inspired than its accomplishments: the vast amount of time it spends doing nothing in particular.

headline.main: Senate Prepares to Wrap Up Sluggish 2013
